Detailed Description

Component Manager Communication Type.

Structure used to store a service callback and its context There is one list of service callback per channel. A same duo (service-callback, context) can be registered on several channels: In this case, the entry is duplicated in each channel list. (Later, this entry could be shared through each channel). 'count' is an "usage count": when equal to zero, the entry can be freed.
